Package: mcmseq
Type: Package
Title: Negative Binomial GLM and GLMM using MCMC
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Brian Vestal, Camille Moore, Elizabeth Wynn
Maintainer: Brian Vestal <vestalb@njhealth.org>
Description: A set of MCMC samplers for NB GLM or GLMM.  These were specifically designed for use with RNA-Seq data.
